tr.th: Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us

tr.td: All results are within normal limits except for a mildly elevated creatinine, which may indicate reduced kidney function. Glucose and HbA1c are at the upper end of normal, suggesting good glycemic control but continued monitoring is advised. No acute abnormalities detected; recommend follow-up of renal function.
